The configurator allows you to associate specific item attributes to configured items. To manage attributes:

1.  Enable Attributes management from the Configurator Setup
2.  Enter Attribute Values in Characteristic and in Characteristic Values


<img width="" src="https://docs.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000340-0/Attributes1_ENU.png"><br>


<img width="" src="https://docs.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000340-0/Attributes2_ENU.png"><br>

The configured items show the attribute values according to the value of the characteristics used. Functionality available only if you use the configurator to generate item codes.

<img width="" src="https://docs.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000340-0/Attributes3_ENU.png"><br>

